# Hydromart internal sweeps (busybox crond). Times are the container's TZ (UTC by
# default — set TZ on the scheduler service to shift). Logs go to the container.
#
# Place orders for all due recurring subscriptions — hourly.
0 * * * * sh /scripts/sweep.sh subscriptions/process-due
# "Time to refill" reorder reminders — daily at 08:00.
0 8 * * * sh /scripts/sweep.sh orders/reminders/reorder
# UU PDP retention: purge proof-of-delivery records past the window — daily at 03:15.
15 3 * * * sh /scripts/sweep.sh proofs/purge-expired delivery:3006
